:"eae1cb03047645737d646849ad86681080a23cc2","tid":1456543,"uid":279616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係仇警，大家一定要清楚知道點解要清算警隊。警暴（濫捕、濫告、不依法規）係暴政一部分，唔全面改革警隊、監警制度，只會令目前同將來爭取雙普選更加舉步維艱<br />\n<br />\n所以，絕對唔需要否認自己係針對警隊，針對警隊就係對準政權。唔通你淨係針對林鄭、唔針對政制，就會有雙普選？<br />\n<br />\n#罷工罷巿罷買<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與全港三罷<br />\n#各區集會<br />\n#出核彈麻包袋都唔割蓆<br />\n#直至政府跪低<br />\n#解散警隊<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動"},{"pid":"e673706ab219d18f21129f1c5c9679338a145b85","tid":1456543,"uid":3255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:36:43.000Z","msg":"佢要清, 如果多人, 一定用船"},{"pid":"753c811f33473de20e489275ae8f2100c6293c5a","tid":1456543,"uid":9021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e673706ab219d18f21129f1c5c9679338a145b85","tid":1456543,"uid":3255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:36:43.000Z","msg":"佢要清, 如果多人, 一定用船"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:37:36.000Z","msg":"兩傘嗰時港鐵一車車運啲狗入去，大家仲記唔記得"},{"pid":"064553caa692ab820c8849e2cf29a0cdf415690a","tid":1456543,"uid":26179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e98b8870cbee79320300eed1c86b279b1d73552","tid":1456543,"uid":9021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ffa05111cb91bd709a40ea4056380e557cc1f49","tid":1456543,"uid":26179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11ae07a6ebc211202afab892c37cbfd6b5651087","tid":1456543,"uid":116914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:27:54.000Z","msg":"圍魏救趙"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:28:43.000Z","msg":"封增援高效啲<br />\n主要因為大嶼山陸路得一條"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:36:10.000Z","msg":"唔好唔記得，閪鐵可以一車車咁車班狗入去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:37:37.000Z","msg":"呢個都要提防"},{"pid":"e546f87c7be035c1d1b27262e8c8d7587883d3ed","tid":1456543,"uid":279567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:37:56.000Z","msg":"pu